                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Tis easy, if soloing u aggro kite.<br /><br />Only first two mobs on left required split FD pull, all others single pull ... though watch out for wandering mob.<br /><br />Just dooming darkness, CoC, send pet, splurt and BoD as required.<br /><br />Use EQTimers and ensure you leave time for 2 or 3 recasts of doom for when u get resists.<br /><br />If u get resists just run up and down the narrow corridor till u have enuff space to recast doomin. U can climb partially up the wall and this really helps.<br /><br />I did it with run2, but i recommend get run3 twill help.</span id="msg"></font></td>
